    "Of 48,544 terms, 2779 meet the threshold.",
    "For each of the 2779 terms, the total strength of the co-occurrence links with other keywords was calculated.",
    "The keywords with the greatest total link strength were selected.",
    "Furthermore, we selected the network visualisation map for the analysis of the publications.",
    "We use the normalization method drop-down list to determine how the strength of the links between the items in a network is normalized in the layout and clustering techniques used by VOSviewer."
